CREATE TRIGGER Bookstore.trg_Book_Logging ON Bookstore.Book
FOR UPDATE, DELETE, INSERT
AS
BEGIN
SET NOCOUNT ON
IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT TOP 1 1 FROM inserted UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 FROM deleted) RETURN

CREATE TABLE #log
(
    ID uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    Action nvarchar(256),
    TableName nvarchar(256),
    ItemId uniqueidentifier,
    Description nvarchar(max)/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnDefinition Bookstore.Book*/
);

INSERT INTO
    #log
    (
        ID,
        Action,
        TableName,
        ItemId,
        Description/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnList Bookstore.Book*/
    )
SELECT
    ID = newid(),
    Action = CASE
        WHEN inserted.ID IS NOT NULL AND deleted.ID IS NULL THEN 'Insert'
        WHEN inserted.ID IS NULL AND deleted.ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'Delete'
        ELSE 'Update'
    END,
    TableName = 'Bookstore.Book',
    ItemId = COALESCE(inserted.ID, deleted.ID),
    Description = CASE WHEN inserted.ID IS NOT NULL AND deleted.ID IS NULL
        THEN ''	--When inserting, Description is not available (there is no previous state)
        ELSE N'<PREVIOUS'
			+ CASE WHEN inserted.Code <> deleted.Code
                    OR inserted.Code IS NULL AND deleted.Code IS NOT NULL
                    OR inserted.Code IS NOT NULL AND deleted.Code IS NULL
                THEN ' Code="' + REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ISNULL(deleted.Code, ''), '&', '&'), '<', '<'), '>', '>'), '"', '"') + '"'
                ELSE '' END
			+ CASE WHEN inserted.Title <> deleted.Title
                    OR inserted.Title IS NULL AND deleted.Title IS NOT NULL
                    OR inserted.Title IS NOT NULL AND deleted.Title IS NULL
                THEN ' Title="' + REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ISNULL(deleted.Title, ''), '&', '&'), '<', '<'), '>', '>'), '"', '"') + '"'
                ELSE '' END
			/*EntityLoggingInfo LogProperty Bookstore.Book*/
            + ' />'
    END/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnSelect Bookstore.Book*/
FROM
    inserted
    FULL OUTER JOIN deleted ON inserted.ID = deleted.ID
    /*EntityLoggingInfo TempFrom Bookstore.Book*/

INSERT INTO Common.Log (ID, Action, TableName, ItemId, Description)
SELECT ID, Action, TableName, ItemId, Description
FROM #log;

/*EntityLoggingInfo AfterInsertLog Bookstore.Book*/
DROP TABLE #log;
END

AS
BEGIN

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT TOP 1 1 FROM inserted UNION ALL SELECT TOP 1 1 FROM deleted) RETURN

CREATE TABLE #log
(
    ID uniqueidentifier NOT NULL,
    Action nvarchar(256),
    TableName nvarchar(256),
    ItemId uniqueidentifier,
    Description nvarchar(max),
    Old_Detail_BookID uniqueidentifier,
    New_Detail_BookID uniqueidentifier/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnDefinition Bookstore.Comment*/
);

INSERT INTO
    #log
    (
        ID,
        Action,
        TableName,
        ItemId,
        Description,
        Old_Detail_BookID,
        New_Detail_BookID/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnList Bookstore.Comment*/
    )
SELECT
    ID = newid(),
    Action = CASE
        WHEN inserted.ID IS NOT NULL AND deleted.ID IS NULL THEN 'Insert'
        WHEN inserted.ID IS NULL AND deleted.ID IS NOT NULL THEN 'Delete'
        ELSE 'Update'
    END,
    TableName = 'Bookstore.Comment',
    ItemId = COALESCE(inserted.ID, deleted.ID),
    Description = CASE WHEN inserted.ID IS NOT NULL AND deleted.ID IS NULL
        THEN ''	--When inserting, Description is not available (there is no previous state)
        ELSE N'<PREVIOUS'
			+ CASE WHEN inserted.BookID <> deleted.BookID
                    OR inserted.BookID IS NULL AND deleted.BookID IS NOT NULL
                    OR inserted.BookID IS NOT NULL AND deleted.BookID IS NULL
                THEN ' BookID="' + REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ISNULL(CONVERT(NVARCHAR(MAX), deleted.BookID, 126), ''), '&', '&'), '<', '<'), '>', '>'), '"', '"') + '"'
                ELSE '' END
			+ CASE WHEN inserted.Text <> deleted.Text
                    OR inserted.Text IS NULL AND deleted.Text IS NOT NULL

                THEN ' Text="' + REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(ISNULL(deleted.Text, ''), '&', '&'), '<', '<'), '>', '>'), '"', '"') + '"'
                ELSE '' END
			/*EntityLoggingInfo LogProperty Bookstore.Comment*/
            + ' />'
    END,
    Old_Detail_BookID = deleted.BookID,
    New_Detail_BookID = inserted.BookID/*EntityLoggingInfo TempColumnSelect Bookstore.Comment*/
FROM
    inserted
    FULL OUTER JOIN deleted ON inserted.ID = deleted.ID
    /*EntityLoggingInfo TempFrom Bookstore.Comment*/

INSERT INTO Common.Log (ID, Action, TableName, ItemId, Description)

    LogID = ID,
    TableName = 'Bookstore.Book',
    ItemId = Old_Detail_BookID,
    Relation = 'Detail'

    Old_Detail_BookID IS NOT NULL;

    ID = NEWID(),
    LogID = ID,
    TableName = 'Bookstore.Book',

FROM
    #log
WHERE
    New_Detail_BookID IS NOT NULL
    AND (New_Detail_BookID <> Old_Detail_BookID OR Old_Detail_BookID IS NULL);
